ockquote>搵我補習</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真 我搵過好多補習 但都係聽唔明 我個腦真係對住數就好唔靈活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做part a1先"},{"pid":"dc4bc110e4dc30e571f947c4f83759e3ab9508ac","tid":386894,"uid":12415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本人係一個數學好差既人 今年dse得個2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都知會俾大家話有腦就有4 肯做就有4 <br />\n但都想請教下大家有無乜入門方法去pick up返d basic maths concept 我想pickup返d野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我之前都係為做而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鋤完數去問勁人，錯嘅問佢點解，錯多百零二百次你就會記得"},{"pid":"72ca5cd7a06b58fd5520cf9a20c79c3f1a6c2897","tid":386894,"uid":18411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵我補習</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真 我搵過好多補習 但都係聽唔明 我個腦真係對住數就好唔靈活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得2補黎曬鳩氣啦<br />\n講深少少，你都未必明啦<br />\n自己搵教科書<br />\n做曬所有題目<br />\n唔明就問人or上網搵教科書題解<br />\n有個底再慢慢操paper<br />\n<br />\n利伸:2升5"},{"pid":"9cdaf784e37bd29eeac6803b155253bce903fb98","tid":386894,"uid":21292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"by topic 咁做,淨係做part A 既題目先<br />\n你會發現其實每個topic既題目都有pattern 捉<br />\n如果你補過習,suppose 應該已經教過點做同用咩skill<br />\n做做下你開始會知自己做緊嘜<br />\n做哂part A 已經係level 3尾<br />\n執多d簡單既part B 已經夠4"},{"pid":"e7b4f778b475fc35e85c5fd7f8ecfb1ef1f827b2","tid":386894,"uid":125535,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:05:55.000Z","msg":"打開本數學書，由練習做起啦<br />\n做完數學書就做PP，做晒PP就重頭做多次<br />\n諗完唔識要問人，不過又唔可以太依賴人，要自己用腦<br />\n以前最長試過對住條數一個鐘，最後自己諗通左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3557f4b51d632d9bceebe85de881797c1081474","tid":386894,"uid":124552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:13:03.000Z","msg":"將數學書的exercise做曬，佢啲example遮住答案做多次，跟住做past paper的A part同B1，做熟已經4，MC就睇下啲人介紹的方法，例如代數，計算機幫手"},{"pid":"c9233e3f9ba559db8391ec15733b83f8822244d5","tid":386894,"uid":136534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"逐課清concept先：做哂書後面啲練習 易嗰啲可以唔做 ；mc買本練習做 記低錯乜 諗下有咩竅妙嘅方法去解<br />\n仲有盡量靠自己解唔識嘅題目 咁樣印象就會深刻啲"},{"pid":"d4c7190efda6002208aa7a44fd78f24c9a4c5d59","tid":386894,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:35:19.000Z","msg":"拎返中一至中三嘅書出黎睇<br />\n確保識晒點由一條therom prove 另一條therom，熟晒啲condition<br />\n學好代數<br />\n跟住學一次中四至中六嘅野<br />\n跟住做PP，睇marking學技巧"},{"pid":"e87c093480210609ccff9ab11e8192397d955258","tid":386894,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"慢慢黎 基本學起<br />\n操paper 同操paper<br />\n<br />\n利申 CE maths E -&gt; AL m&amp;s B"},{"pid":"d26ad750d4ee8c642250433124006f75bb1af477","tid":386894,"uid":143678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵我補習</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真 我搵過好多補習 但都係聽唔明 我個腦真係對住數就好唔靈活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得2補黎曬鳩氣啦<br />\n講深少少，你都未必明啦<br />\n自己搵教科書<br />\n做曬所有題目<br />\n唔明就問人or上網搵教科書題解<br />\n有個底再慢慢操paper<br />\n<br />\n利伸:2升5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好啦我會努力咖啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a55bad2aba36a9520db2e8f7fcfd88ee2c5fcf0","tid":386894,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:43:08.000Z","msg":"herman yeung呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇herman yeung呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n搵數學補習之前睇左佢套大檸樂補底片先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375b5ec80926494dfba71a5d4d5b20a34f29055d","tid":386894,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本人係一個數學好差既人 今年dse得個2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都知會俾大家話有腦就有4 肯做就有4 <br />\n但都想請教下大家有無乜入門方法去pick up返d basic maths concept 我想pickup返d野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我之前都係為做而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補迷離哥哥"},{"pid":"1e5aa03a452cb4de01d9ee25df51d3d7a683fa2c","tid":386894,"uid":136618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"Mc35題以上<br />\n<br />\nA1最多失6分左右，其他盡力做，多數都有4"},{"pid":"800cd23d34502865fef1bbd47e87cc0ade796f1f","tid":386894,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本人係一個數學好差既人 今年dse得個2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都知會俾大家話有腦就有4 肯做就有4 <br />\n但都想請教下大家有無乜入門方法去pick up返d basic maths concept 我想pickup返d野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我之前都係為做而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補迷離哥哥</blockquote><br />\n呢個真"},{"pid":"ef315443db07fad0c26825597de5c648dad14f59","tid":386894,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本人係一個數學好差既人 今年dse得個2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都知會俾大家話有腦就有4 肯做就有4 <br />\n但都想請教下大家有無乜入門方法去pick up返d basic maths concept 我想pickup返d野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我之前都係為做而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補迷離哥哥</blockquote><br />\n呢個真</blockquote><br />\n小弟16dse得lv2 <br />\n17年補完迷離哥哥有5**"},{"pid":"01e9f1827c0429804bd470e53c615dd87e0f9f5c","tid":386894,"uid":36014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"做市面上既by topic exercise<br />\n有本幾好<br />\n廢事賣廣告<br />\n想知再講<br />\n然後做20年by year<br />\n咁都冇五既話你應該要去驗腦<br />\n利申5&gt;5星"},{"pid":"180e1132a97be4891988577b6b094f34d92367e6","tid":386894,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做市面上既by topic exercise<br />\n有本幾好<br />\n廢事賣廣告<br />\n想知再講<br />\n然後做20年by year<br />\n咁都冇五既話你應該要去驗腦<br />\n利申5&gt;5星</blockquote><br />\n想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a8a8f291647265e2448b7f873a6415b0db254e","tid":386894,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本人係一個數學好差既人 今年dse得個2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都知會俾大家話有腦就有4 肯做就有4 <br />\n但都想請教下大家有無乜入門方法去pick up返d basic maths concept 我想pickup返d野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我之前都係為做而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補迷離哥哥</blockquote><br />\n呢個真</blockquote><br />\n小弟16dse得lv2 <br />\n17年補完迷離哥哥有5**</blockquote><br />\n但迷離哥哥得 5*"},{"pid":"00dab5b05ed78c6cd04340e1df48263832297432","tid":386894,"uid":133539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"第一年數學2，retake上四。<br />\n我覺得最大問題通常係自己跟唔上教書嘅速度。有時老師教到c，你都仲未明a點嚟，但係又要焗住聽。舊嘅未清新嘅又係咁嚟，自然好難學得好。解決方法係自己做數，唔好理其他人嘅速度，遇到唔明就上網查資料查到自己明為止。始終自己先係最清楚自己情況嘅人<br />\n其次就係知識碎片化。有好多嘢自己唔係唔識，而係太散，組織唔到係埋一齊，睇唔穿當中關係，溫書時自然就多咗嘢溫。將相關知識組合埋一齊溫就會易溫好多。<br />\n另外就係要搵兩個或以上嘅人做你嘅導師。同一條數最好問兩個人，可能會有唔同解法。可能當中一個你容易明啲。<br />\n以上就係我嘅心得，希望幫到你"}]}